privacy@giggleacademy.com
.
These rights may be limited and subject to exceptions in some situations - for example, where we can demonstrate we have a legal requirement to process your personal data.
·
Request Access to the personal information we process about you: You can request access to the information we have collected from you. You can do this by contacting us at
privacy@giggleacademy.com
.
We will provide you with a copy of the data we process abo
ut you. To comply with your request, we may ask you to verify your identity.
·
Request a rectification of your personal data: If you believe that the information we have collected is incorrect or incomplete, you may contact us so we can update it and keep your data accurate.
·
Object to the processing of your personal data: you may request that we no longer process your personal data in certain circumstances.
·
Right to portability: You can also request us to provide your information in a structured way so you can send it to another service provider.
·
Right to withdrawn consent: if we rely on consent for processing data, you can request to withdraw your consent at any time.
The withdrawal of consent does not affect the lawfulness of processing based on consent before its withdrawal
·
Request to erase your personal data: you may request the erasure of your personal data, including where such personal data would no longer be necessary to achieve the purposes for which it was collected.
